      "content": "sometimes i look at my screen and i feel like i don't even exist. i work all day, i eat, i sleep, but it feels like i'm just a ghost drifting through a city of people who would never even look up if i was standing right in front of them. it's just... so quiet. i feel like if i just stopped showing up, one day the silence would just be permanent and no one would even realize the gap i left.",
